4. Summary

âœ… Eviction thresholds prevent memory and disk exhaustion.
âœ… Garbage collection keeps disk storage healthy by cleaning up unused images.
âœ… Properly tuned KubeletConfig is critical for OpenShift node reliability.
âœ… The thresholds are based on percentages of available resources + real-world OpenShift stability experience.

